h3#snippet Code snippet
p
	| The TabNavigator has three important parts:
ul.ch-list
	li 
		| The 
		strong tablist
		|  is a list of links each pointing to the content.
	li 
		| The 
		strong tabpanel
		|  is the container of the one part of the content.
	li 
		| The 
		strong tabs
		|  is the group of the tabpanels.
p 
	| The content could be in the HTML or you can load it via Ajax call.

div
