h4#loading-async-content Loading asynchronous content
p
	| The component can load async content. To work, the link in 
	strong tablist
	|  must have a URL where the content is. Instead of:
pre
	| <li><a href="#tab1">Tab 1</a></li>
p
	| You have to put the URL in the 
	code href
	|  atrribute:
pre
	| <li><a href="example.html">Tab 1</a></li>
p
	| You can add some callbacks function: 
	code contentLoad
	|  and 
	code contentError
	| .

h4#select-and-getselect select and getSelect
p
	| The 
	code select
	|  method allow you to show a tab. The 
	code getSelect
	|  method allow you to know which tab is selected. It returns an integer that represents the tab order starting at 
	code 1
